        <div class="content">
            <img src="/images/blood-donation1.jpg" alt="Donate Blood">
            <h2>Our Nation Requires 4 Crore Units of Blood</h2>
            <p>
                Blood is life. Every two seconds, someone in the world needs blood. Unfortunately, while the demand for blood is high, 
                only a fraction of eligible individuals donate. Blood donation is one of the most selfless acts of kindness that saves 
                lives and supports families during critical medical situations. Remember, there is no substitute for human blood.
            </p>
            <p>
                By donating blood, you not only save lives but also help maintain sufficient blood reserves for emergencies such as 
                surgeries, accidents, and chronic illnesses. Every drop counts, and your contribution makes a world of difference.
            </p>
            <button class="donor-btn" onclick="beADonor()">Be a Donor</button>
        </div>

        <!-- Additional content section -->
        <div class="benefits">
            <h3>Benefits of Donating Blood</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>You save up to three lives with one donation.</li>
                <li>Regular blood donation improves your heart health by reducing harmful iron levels in your body.</li>
                <li>It enhances the production of new red blood cells in your body.</li>
                <li>Blood donors are prioritized for transfusions in emergencies.</li>
